{"tid":16271,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[壁球女團世錦賽] 8強 香港 VS 馬來西亞 12am","createTime":"2016-12-01T11:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T11:12:06.000Z","uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"53b6df2f62d92345cf3422e08e1cfc604a3e27bc","tid":16271,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://68.media.tumblr.com/7c4c62670728957576c35c84b2282168/tumblr_inline_ohi1uukeby1s38j9i_1280.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F68.media.tumblr.com%2F7c4c62670728957576c35c84b2282168%2Ftumblr_inline_ohi1uukeby1s38j9i_1280.png&h=0a79c792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n女子世界壁球團體錦標賽2016正於法國巴黎舉行，今屆賽事第四種籽香港女子代表隊，成員包括歐詠芝，陳浩鈴，廖梓苓及湯芷穎力圖突破於上屆打入四強的歷史佳績。<br />\n<br />\n香港隊在小組中已先後擊敗德國，日本及西班牙。於最後一場的小組賽事中迎戰東道主法國，陳浩鈴率先上場以直落三局輕取對手，歐詠芝及廖梓苓在隨後兩場以1-3落敗，但仍帶領香港以小組次名出線八強。<br />\n<br />\n他們將於香港時間星期五凌晨12時迎戰三號種籽馬來西亞。"},{"pid":"e6fd8ddb386babf87ab38f327f5515263e69e957","tid":16271,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T11:12:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtube.com/watch?v=-CTJAIHByzo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D-CTJAIHByzo&d=AECyLZWdcqpY%2FGgvZN2GpJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=d5c52a43\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtube.com/watch?v=-CTJAIHByzo</a><br />\n官方直播link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}